---
title: OKD - Enterprise Open Source Kubernetes Distribution
---

<% content_for :header do %>
<h1 class="animated fadeInDown delay" style="font-size: 48px;">
  The Enterprise Open Source Kubernetes Distribution
</h1>
<p class="animated fadeInUp delay">OKD is the upstream community project that powers <a href="https://www.openshift.com" class="headerlink">OpenShift</a>. Built around a core of Docker container packaging and Kubernetes container cluster management, OKD is also augmented by application lifecycle management functionality and DevOps tooling. OKD provides a complete open source container application platform.</p>
<% end %>

